{
  "stem": "3103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a child, I remember she covered the tablecloths with special-- the tables with special cloths.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was washed, which my mother did not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had separate dishes, and I was very impressed with that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the Seder nacht, we were about 25 people, which my grandfather, [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Motel, ?] was sitting in a white-- I don't know what they call it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's not a robe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kittel, the white kittel-- not just sitting, but leaning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all were just so hypnotized by the things what were going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no movement and no speaking back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You sat like this till 1 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we enjoyed every moment of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the end, we made the journey back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is the best I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She made special thing that I enjoyed, not for Passover, was a Easter cake with chocolate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I used to come visit, she used to hide it because she knew it's going to be gone in an hour.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she gave me every day another extra piece, and I loved it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, I don't remember anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, as I say, I was impressed with special different dishes that you never used during-- if there was no holiday.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was impressed with the centerpiece.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was impressed the way all the uncles-- they were younger then-- were dressed in the little suits with the ties and with us made special new clothes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If it starts with the dress to new shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you look forwards for this time of the year because you knew you were always getting something new.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rosh Hashanah, we used to spend at home because of the traveling and Yom Kippur is so close.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
